<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavarṣaṁbu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lu 108<unclear>1</unclear> nēṁṭi śrīmadanaṁ 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ttavarmmadēvara pravarddhamā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na vijarājyasaṁvatsa 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>raṁbulu <unclear>5</unclear> śrāhi kanya śu 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kla 10 budhavāramuna [E] 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṟadapaṁpuna tālāṁḻa cō 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḻagaṁggamādhavadēvara gu 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḍi sthānāpatitanamu kaḍa 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>pāka puruṣōttamabhaṭlaku 
<lb n="11"/>Īyaya koḍku vidvajjanapri 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ya brahmamārāyaniki <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>dulanāgamanāyakuni koḍku 
<lb n="14"/>Eṟapōtanāyakuṁḍu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> dēva 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ra divyasannidhānamunaṁdu Ā 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>caṁdrārkkasthāyigā dhārāpūrvvaka 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>mu sēsenu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> dīni kahitamu tala 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṁcināru gaṁgakaṟuta vēyi ka 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>yilala vadhasēsināru 
</p>

